description: Re-development of site from educational facilities to residential comprising conversion of the existing 'convent' building to provide  21x1 bedroom and 16x2 bedroom apartments and erection of 2x3 storey blocks of 8x2 bedroom and 4x1 bedroom  apartments, 1x3 storey block of 4x2 bedroom and 2x1 bedroom apartments and a pair of 4 bedroom semi-detached houses fronting Burcharbro Road. Provision of 95 car parking spaces.
